00:42:04.759 --> 00:42:09.347
Lihat, saya tak berniat jahat,
tapi jangan datang dekat kami, Elise.


434
00:42:09.513 --> 00:42:11.223
Jangan datang dekat.

435
00:42:12.391 --> 00:42:13.893
Christian.

